00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,400
Anything else?

299
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,000
Some good news.

300
00:18:38,559 --> 00:18:40,720
Thanks to that fake news,

301
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:42,200
my endorsement was signed today.

302
00:18:42,559 --> 00:18:44,079
You'll be free soon.

303
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,640
Tell him not to worry.

304
00:19:06,279 --> 00:19:07,598
After shooting the last scene,

305
00:19:07,599 --> 00:19:09,240
we'll wrap up for today.

306
00:19:10,759 --> 00:19:11,160
Hey.

307
00:19:11,559 --> 00:19:12,720
Why is he back again?

308
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:15,600
I don't get why you got your ear pierced.

309
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,520
Are we dropping the later scenes?

310
00:19:17,759 --> 00:19:18,759
Of course not.

311
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,080
I'm tough.

312
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:21,856
The swelling will be gone tomorrow.

313
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,880
Besides,

314
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,080
who looks at ears?

315
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,480
Why?

316
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:27,279
This is the big screen.

317
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,400
I just wanted to.

318
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,400
You...

319
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,680
You always act on impulse.

320
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,640
Qin Yao really doesn't keep you in check.

321
00:19:36,799 --> 00:19:37,799
So reckless.

322
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,640
Hey, Xiao Chen.

323
00:19:49,825 --> 00:19:50,825
Let's go.

324
00:19:50,949 --> 00:19:51,949
Let's go.

325
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,279
Weibo is already a mess.

326
00:19:57,039 --> 00:19:58,279
And he still smiles at you?

327
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,720
And you too.

328
00:19:59,759 --> 00:20:01,240
Why even respond?

329
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:03,000
Really...

330
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:10,120
After filming, come alone to
Room 1638 at the Grand Hyatt.

331
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,799
I'll wait for you there.

332
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:15,920
Let's go.

333
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:48,680
Okay.
That's it.

334
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:52,039
Surprised I'm here?

335
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,319
Too many eyes at the crew hotel.

336
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:56,320
Some things are safer said here.

337
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,400
Nice earring, right?

338
00:21:06,839 --> 00:21:07,879
Why?

339
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:10,200
I wanted to match you.

340
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,960
But it really hurt.

341
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:15,920
I only got through it by thinking of you.

342
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,320
Hey.

343
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:23,079
I booked this room.

344
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:25,599
Can you two flirt after I leave?

345
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,960
So

346
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,720
what is this?

347
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,440
Someone

348
00:21:32,519 --> 00:21:35,079
insisted I explain it to you myself.

349
00:21:35,559 --> 00:21:36,759
The marriage news is fake.

350
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:38,775
The trending topic was bought by a rival.

351
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:39,999
I hope you won't overthink it.

352
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,240
I won't.

353
00:21:42,319 --> 00:21:44,279
I never take gossip to heart.

354
00:21:44,799 --> 00:21:45,799
Still,

355
00:21:46,359 --> 00:21:47,479
thank you.

356
00:21:48,039 --> 00:21:49,039
No need.

357
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,599
I keep my promises.

358
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:52,360
If I promise something,
I see it through.

359
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,480
Look how worried you were.

360
00:21:54,759 --> 00:21:55,759
Look at him.

361
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:57,720
Much more mature and calm than you.

362
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,720
Fine.

363
00:22:04,079 --> 00:22:05,599
I won't be a third wheel.

364
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:07,360
Right.

365
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,840
I've handled the media.

366
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:11,600
I hope this little incident

367
00:22:11,799 --> 00:22:13,559
won't affect our agreement.

368
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,880
I'm leaving.

369
00:22:21,759 --> 00:22:22,920
What agreement?

370
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,720
We're in the same industry.

371
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,119
What else could it be?

372
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:34,880
A clean breakup.

373
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,000
Let's go.

374
00:23:00,079 --> 00:23:01,399
[You think you're] still filming?

375
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,640
Don't you think

376
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,839
we're more dramatic than the show?

377
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,680
What are you doing?

378
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,480
Try it.

379
00:23:17,319 --> 00:23:18,399
Red wine flavor.

380
00:23:48,519 --> 00:23:49,519
Hello, Senior.

381
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:50,800
It's me.

382
00:23:51,079 --> 00:23:52,079
Fang Chi.

383
00:23:53,279 --> 00:23:55,879
I remember you have a
therapy room in the CBD.

384
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,880
Can I borrow it for a while?

385
00:24:01,079 --> 00:24:02,079
Okay.

386
00:24:02,799 --> 00:24:03,799
Thanks, Senior.

387
00:24:23,359 --> 00:24:24,359
Secretary Feng.

388
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:27,359
Notify every patient except Gao Zhun

389
00:24:28,039 --> 00:24:29,159
that starting next week,

390
00:24:29,279 --> 00:24:30,679
sessions will be at a new location.

391
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,720
I'll send you the address later.

392
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,280
[Gao Zhun: Can I see your earlier today?]

393
00:24:45,759 --> 00:24:47,000
[Unpin]

394
00:25:29,559 --> 00:25:30,559
Hello?

395
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,279
Fang...

396
00:25:31,559 --> 00:25:32,559
Dr. Fang.

397
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:34,080
You finally answered.

398
00:25:34,599 --> 00:25:35,599
Where did you go?

399
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,599
Why is no one at your home?

400
00:25:37,799 --> 00:25:38,839
The clinic is empty too.

401
00:25:40,839 --> 00:25:42,079
Did something happen to you?

402
00:25:47,759 --> 00:25:48,759
You...

403
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:50,880
Why aren't you speaking?

404
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,480
Are you...

405
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,400
abandoning me?

406
00:26:07,799 --> 00:26:08,839
Mr. Gao.

407
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,640
Your treatment is over.

408
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,519
But I'm not healed yet.

409
00:26:20,599 --> 00:26:22,240
Your nightmare is gone.

410
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:25,799
Mr. Gao.

411
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,519
You'll get better with time.

412
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,559
Please let me see you.

413
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:34,920
Whatever we need to say,

414
00:26:35,599 --> 00:26:36,639
let's say it face to face.

415
00:26:37,759 --> 00:26:38,759
Sorry.

416
00:26:40,039 --> 00:26:41,279
This is not right.

417
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,200
I'm the doctor.

418
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:45,640
You're the patient.

419
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:48,680
I've already

420
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,279
made too many mistakes.

421
00:26:55,799 --> 00:26:56,519
You did nothing wrong.

422
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:57,759
I wanted it.

423
00:26:58,240 --> 00:26:59,240
Enough.

424
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,960
Gao Zhun.

425
00:27:03,039 --> 00:27:04,079
Listen to me.

426
00:27:06,799 --> 00:27:08,519
You need to move forward.

427
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,000
You mean

428
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,160
we're over...?

429
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,759
When did we ever begin?

430
00:27:29,319 --> 00:27:30,599
Treat it as a dream.

431
00:27:30,799 --> 00:27:31,799
No.

432
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,920
If it's a dream, I can't wake up.

433
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:36,920
Please.

434
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,400
Don't.

435
00:27:37,559 --> 00:27:38,759
Don't leave me.

436
00:27:40,079 --> 00:27:41,079
Once a week.

437
00:27:41,119 --> 00:27:43,119
Even once every ten days or half a month.

438
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:46,840
I don't like you anymore.

439
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,680
I'll stop liking you, okay?

440
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,239
Just let me see you.

441
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,920
Don't leave me.

442
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,000
Don't...

443
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,720
don't force me...

444
00:28:55,119 --> 00:28:56,119
Please don't...

445
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,200
We can't...

446
00:29:05,039 --> 00:29:06,519
keep making this mistake.

447
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,880
Cut.

448
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:19,920
Where is he?

449
00:29:20,839 --> 00:29:21,839
He cried too hard.

450
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,680
He's in the restroom calming down.

451
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,000
Don't.

452
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:49,799
There are people outside.

453
00:29:58,559 --> 00:29:59,960
Your eyes are red from crying.

454
00:30:01,732 --> 00:30:02,972
The show is fake.

455
00:30:03,359 --> 00:30:04,919
You and I are real.

456
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,960
I know.

457
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,359
But Gao Zhun's pain...

458
00:30:16,360 --> 00:30:17,360
I...

459
00:30:19,079 --> 00:30:20,159
I understand it completely.

460
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,840
If you understand Gao Zhun,

461
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,279
then you should know.

462
00:30:27,359 --> 00:30:29,479
Fang Chi's love never changed.

463
00:30:30,839 --> 00:30:31,959
And off set,

464
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,920
I've always loved you too.

465
00:30:44,319 --> 00:30:45,960
Are they calling us for pickup shots?

466
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,000
No.

467
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,680
It's Feng Yunting.

468
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,080
My engagement to Mr. Zhen

469
00:31:04,279 --> 00:31:05,359
and marriage

470
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,240
are complete nonsense.

471
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,319
The so-called leak

472
00:31:09,839 --> 00:31:11,239
is now being handled by the police.

473
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:13,480
Is this just your side of the story?

474
00:31:13,519 --> 00:31:15,319
Does Mr. Zhen feel the same?

475
00:31:17,079 --> 00:31:18,079
In fact,

476
00:31:19,079 --> 00:31:20,799
Zhen Xin and I have broken up.

477
00:31:24,119 --> 00:31:25,839
Because of the fake marriage news,

478
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,560
we've both thought a lot.

479
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,160
About this relationship,

480
00:31:32,079 --> 00:31:33,279
we both need some space.

481
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,960
Who proposed the breakup?

482
00:31:37,279 --> 00:31:38,279
I did.

483
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,240
He agreed.

484
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:48,080
So this was your agreement.

485
00:31:52,279 --> 00:31:53,479
Miss Feng really
had to suffer for this...

486
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:54,480
Zhang Zhun.

487
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:59,200
There are things I must tell you myself.

488
00:32:02,599 --> 00:32:03,599
I love you.

489
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,000
Not Fang Chi.

490
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,680
It's me.

491
00:32:09,279 --> 00:32:10,559
Zhen Xin loves you.

492
00:32:24,559 --> 00:32:25,559
I know.

493
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:29,519
I love you too.

494
00:32:45,839 --> 00:32:46,959
I'm at the crew hotel.

495
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,080
Send me your room number.

496
00:32:48,359 --> 00:32:49,359
I'll come to you.

497
00:32:53,359 --> 00:32:55,159
Why are you here?

498
00:32:56,039 --> 00:32:57,399
Is something wrong?

499
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:02,320
[Best Actor Zhen Xin's
Set Romance Turns Sour.]

500
00:33:02,480 --> 00:33:03,799
[The Third Party Is a Man?]

501
00:33:04,279 --> 00:33:06,055
[Zhen Xin and Zhang Zhun
bonded through filming.]

502
00:33:06,079 --> 00:33:07,919
[Matching couple
earrings on their left ears.]

503
00:33:08,039 --> 00:33:09,239
[Who is Zhang Zhun?]

504
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:11,039
[Couple earrings? That's hilarious.]

505
00:33:11,079 --> 00:33:12,815
[If he didn't hype himself,
no one would know him.]

506
00:33:12,839 --> 00:33:15,439
[If Zhen Xin is gay, I'm unstanning.]

507
00:33:15,599 --> 00:33:16,759
[That's disgusting.]

508
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:19,598
[Is every guy trying to get
famous by queerbaiting now?]

509
00:33:19,599 --> 00:33:21,119
[Dig up everything on Zhang Zhun.]

510
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,000
Last night,

511
00:37:38,119 --> 00:37:39,839
I actually had a gift for you.

512
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:44,719
Pick one.

513
00:37:47,519 --> 00:37:48,519
Choose carefully.

514
00:37:48,599 --> 00:37:50,360
This is my first gift to you.

515
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:52,199
Oh.

516
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,760
This one.

517
00:38:09,159 --> 00:38:10,159
These two are a pair.

518
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,680
You and I can wear them as a pair.
